{"tid":1045470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嚇死！超大鱷魚現身美國喬治亞州 然後就被安樂死了...","createTime":"2019-03-03T15:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T01:16:04.000Z","uid":32511,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"136298e12797d77a3280a2348e8df4011351f418","tid":1045470,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T15:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phphWqORn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phphWqORn.jpg&h=acf56dd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這鱷魚超級大！美國喬治亞州自然資源部（Georgia DNR）最近在一處灌溉溝渠內，發現一條身長13英尺（約4公尺）、重達700磅（約318公斤）的短吻鱷，牠最後的下場是被安樂死。<br />\n <br />\n據《福斯新聞》報導，喬治亞州DNR發言人卡明斯（Melissa Cummings）表示，這個發現顯示出鱷魚真的可以長得如此大隻。而鱷魚長到那麼大的唯一方法，就是避開人類。<br />\n <br />\n野生動物學家豪澤（Brent Howze）與超大鱷魚的合影，在網路上受到不少網友質疑，認為這根本是修圖，但豪澤保證一切都是真的。<br />\n <br />\n豪澤估計該隻鱷魚已在溝渠內待了將近一個星期，這是相當不尋常的行為。而且由於鱷魚大到卡在裡面，當局不得不出動重型設備將牠吊出。<br />\n <br />\n卡明斯說，自然資源部協助鱷魚脫困後，發現牠身體上似乎有舊的槍傷，在確認其身體狀況不佳後，最後鱷魚便被安樂死了。"},{"pid":"a8cbbbb8ab12875dd3d92722e1ec7293245fdee0","tid":1045470,"uid":16676,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T15:23:53.000Z","msg":"手袋👜皮鞋👞😍"},{"pid":"f80c9c42f66d09b4b3ef112dc576928ead4a1ca6","tid":1045470,"uid":7741,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T15:26:00.000Z","msg":"大鄉里第一次人姓cummings<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d546195f16309d4581293fe9f643b592ba609bcb","tid":1045470,"uid":75050,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T15:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/233047_6df5bc497df96cdc46a014335acca3f7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F233047_6df5bc497df96cdc46a014335acca3f7.png&h=45d7a066&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25a11db1a9cf4597581ce10220e9a8c2f3015ab9","tid":1045470,"uid":224375